Class AdminListFragment

java.lang.Object
androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
com.kraken.krakenhax.AdminListFragment
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.activity.result.ActivityResultCaller, androidx.lifecycle.HasDefaultViewModelProviderFactory, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner
public class AdminListFragment extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
Admin fragment to display the lists of entrants, organizers, and events. Will later display images and notifications. Allows the admin to delete profiles.

    • getNotifications

      public void getNotifications(ArrayList<Profile> profileList)
      Gets a list of notifications sent to entrants from organizers. Gets an arrayList of notifications by iterating through an arrayList of entrant profiles and getting any notifications in their Notification Collections. Displays the notifications through an ArrayAdapter for the notifications class and sets them up in a ListView.
      Parameters:
      profileList - Takes an arrayList of entrant Profiles to get notifications from.
